title: Halloween Props
description: Set of spooky props for interactive Halloween wallpapers, special game editions

Bat / bones / broom / candelabra / candles / cat / cleaver / coffin / eyeball / fences / fireworks / ghost / grass / hat / chain / knife / lanterns / moon / nail / owl / planks / pots / potions / pumpkins / rocks / scroll / scythe / skulls / spear / spider / spiderwebs / spike / tombstones / torches / tree / zombie hands Particle effects and animations for some props.
